criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Agreement to participate in the research from their selves and their legal guardians
             (by signing assent form and consent form);

          -  Have a clinical diagnosis of CP done by a neuropediatric clinician with non-
             progressive etiology;

          -  GMFCS levels I to IV;

          -  MACS I and IV.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Lack of understanding of the the tasks. The understanding of the task will be
             evaluated through five attempts of each task in VR, because even with low IQ a large
             part of the adolescents can understand virtual tasks and interact with improvement of
             performance;

          -  Motor difficulties that impede the completing of the virtual tasks;

          -  Cardiac diseases (because of the HRV assessment).
